LinearReferencingMethod.gml:description: Absolute measured depth from top of borehole or sounding in meters. Measurements are cumulative 3D distance along the borehole/sounding centerline from the first coordinate (typically top of hole or rig datum) proceeding downward through the hole. Suitable for vertical, slanted, and deviated boreholes and soundings.
LinearReferencingMethod.diggs:name: trueMeters
